import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1, x2):
    v0 = jnp.abs(x2)
    v1 = jnp.add(x2, x2)
    v2 = jnp.add(v1, x2)
    v3 = jnp.minimum(x0, v1)
    v4 = jnp.cos(v3)
    v5 = jnp.subtract(x0, v1)
    v6 = jnp.add(v4, v4)
    v7 = jnp.subtract(v2, v6)
